===
TOA
===
toa
+++
Get FTC-related information from The Orange Alliance. If no subcommand
is specified, the `team` subcommand is inferred, and the argument is
taken as a team number.
::
   `{prefix}toa 5667` - show information on team 5667, Robominers
team
++++
Get information on an FTC team by number.
::
   `{prefix}toa team 12670` - show information on team 12670, Eclipse
